tiaraRipMib.description: This file contains Tiara's enterprise specific MIB module for RIP implementation

tiaraRoutingEnable.name: tiaraRoutingEnable
tiaraRoutingEnable.description: This variable is used to globally enable/disable Routing. DEFVAL { false}

tiaraRipGlobalEnable.name: tiaraRipGlobalEnable
tiaraRipGlobalEnable.description: This variable is used to globally enable/disable RIP. The per- interface enable/disable override the setting of this variable

tiaraRipGlobalUseTrustedNeighbour.name: tiaraRipGlobalUseTrustedNeighbour
tiaraRipGlobalUseTrustedNeighbour.description: This variable is used to enable/disable the use of Trusted Neighbour

tiaraRipGlobalVersion.name: tiaraRipGlobalVersion
tiaraRipGlobalVersion.description: version of RIP to be used. per-interface send and receive versions override the setting of this variable

tiaraRipIfConfTable.name: tiaraRipIfConfTable
tiaraRipIfConfTable.description: A list of RIP interfaces and Per-Interface RIP Configuration Table

tiaraRipIfConfEntry.name: tiaraRipIfConfEntry
tiaraRipIfConfEntry.description: A single RIP interface and its configuration parameters

tiaraRipIfConfIpAddr.name: tiaraRipIfConfIpAddr
tiaraRipIfConfIpAddr.description: The IP Address assigned to the given RIP interface. This variable is also used to index into the table

tiaraRipIfConfAuthString.name: tiaraRipIfConfAuthString
tiaraRipIfConfAuthString.description: The string to be used as the authentication key Setting this string to NULL value has the effect of disabling authentication. Setting this string to a non-value has the effect enabling authentication, with the value of the string used as authentication string. By default, the value of the string is null and hence authentication is disabled

tiaraRipIfConfDefaultAnnounceEnable.name: tiaraRipIfConfDefaultAnnounceEnable
tiaraRipIfConfDefaultAnnounceEnable.description: Used to enable/disable announcing RIP default route

tiaraRipIfConfEnable.name: tiaraRipIfConfEnable
tiaraRipIfConfEnable.description: enable/disable RIP for this interface. The value of this variable overrides the value of the Global variable, tiaraRipGlobalEnable

tiaraRipIfConfPassiveEnable.name: tiaraRipIfConfPassiveEnable
tiaraRipIfConfPassiveEnable.description: suppress/do not suppress sending of routing updates

tiaraRipIfConfReceiveVersion.name: tiaraRipIfConfReceiveVersion
tiaraRipIfConfReceiveVersion.description: configuration variable for RIP receive version for this interface

tiaraRipIfConfSendVersion.name: tiaraRipIfConfSendVersion
tiaraRipIfConfSendVersion.description: configuration variable for RIP send version for this interface
